Interface TrialDataExporter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TrialDataJsonImportExporter

    public interface TrialDataExporter
    The TrialDataExporter interface is implemented by classes that support exporting the trial data to an OutputStream. Known implementing classes are TrialDataJsonImportExporter
